    {
      "instruction": "<p>Line a baking tray with <strong>baking paper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to the baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>cumin seeds</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>cumin chips</strong></p>",
