      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>lamb mince </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
