    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the lamb has slightly browned, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>half</strong> the <strong>diced onion</strong> (save the rest for later!) and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until the onion has started to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
