      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is beginning to soften, add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for a further 4-5 min or until the curry has thickened to a bolognese-like consistency and the lamb is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>fragrant</strong> <strong>lamb curry</strong></p>",
