    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> remaining chopped tomato</strong>, <strong>diced onion </strong>and <strong>chopped chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>to a small bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>and toss – this is your <strong>chilli tomato salad</strong></p>",
